# NOTE: google-services.json is intentionally NOT ignored here.
# It's a client-side config file (the same one that ships inside every
# built APK), so it's fine to commit if this repo is private — and the
# GitHub Actions workflow (.github/workflows/build-apk.yml) needs it
# present in the repo to build. If this repo is or becomes public,
# add "android/app/google-services.json" to this file instead and pass
# it into CI via a GitHub Secret.
